PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice seize cannabis sweets 'aimed at
OL,4,Ckids' along with more than 100 plants
OL,6,FCannabis-infused sweet packaging aimed
OL,7,Fat children has been seized in a
OL,8,Fseries of early morning drug raids.
OL,10,FOfficers from a Lancashire Police task
OL,11,Fforce carried out the raids on an
OL,12,Faddress on Moor Lane in Darwen and a
OL,13,Fproperty on Hollin Bridge Street in
OL,14,FBlackburn, discovering drugs at both
OL,15,Flocations.
OL,17,FAt the Darwen address, officers seized
OL,18,Fa large stash of packaging for
OL,19,Fcannabis-infused sweets which they say
OL,20,Fwas "clearly aimed at children".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
