FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice seize cannabis sweets 'aimed at
OL,4,Ckids' along with more than 100 plants
OL,6,FMuch of the packaging parodied real
OL,7,Fsweet brands, with names like 'Stoner
OL,8,FPatch Kids', 'Trips Ahoy!', and
OL,9,F'Medicated Millions'
OL,11,FOfficers also found a haul of
OL,12,Fcannabis, steroids, and THC vapes at
OL,13,Fthe Moor Lane property.
OL,15,FIn Blackburn, officers discovered a
OL,16,Flarge cannabis farm made up of 118
OL,17,Fplants.
OL,19,FNo arrests have been made in
OL,20,Fconnection with the morning raids.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
