OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice seize cannabis sweets 'aimed at
OL,4,Ckids' along with more than 100 plants
OL,6,FPolice said the raids were carried out
OL,7,Fthanks to intelligence from the
OL,8,Fpublic, helping them remove
OL,9,Fpotentially dangerous drugs and items
OL,10,Ffrom the streets.
OL,12,FBlackburn and Darwen Police posted on
OL,13,FFacebook saying: "This morning, Task
OL,14,FForce and the Neighbourhood Policing
OL,15,Fteam have executed 2 Misuse of Drugs
OL,16,FAct warrants on Moor Lane, Darwen and
OL,17,FHollin Bridge Street, Blackburn.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
