OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice seize cannabis sweets 'aimed at
OL,4,Ckids' along with more than 100 plants
OL,6,F"Numerous items have been seized in
OL,7,Fthe address at Darwen including;
OL,8,Fmultiple THC Vapes, a variety of
OL,9,Fsteroids, and a quantity of Cannabis.
OL,10,FDisconcertingly, within the address,
OL,11,Fofficers have located a significant
OL,12,Famount of packaging for cannabis based
OL,13,Fsweets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
