FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice seize cannabis sweets 'aimed at
OL,4,Ckids' along with more than 100 plants
OL,6,F"This packing is clearly aimed at
OL,7,Fchildren, and we have seen a
OL,8,Fsignificant increase in issues caused
OL,9,Fby these items within the local area.
OL,10,FWithin the address, officers also
OL,11,Flocated a large number of containers
OL,12,Fand labels falsely claiming to be
OL,13,Fmedical cannabis.
OL,15,F"At Hollin Bridge Street, 118 plants
OL,16,Fwere located within the property.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
